---
// The Four Phases section. Used on the home page.
---

<section class="container" id="process">
  <div class="section-title reveal">
    <div class="section-title__label">IV004 — The Process</div>
    <h2 class="section-title__title">Four phases, anchored to <em>the human</em>.</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="phases reveal">
    <div class="phases__list">
      <div class="phase">
        <div class="phase__num">PH / 01</div>
        <div class="phase__name">Human Foundation</div>
        <div class="phase__desc">
          Every project begins and ends with the people it is for. We define the audiences,
          the operational teams, and the stakeholders whose lives the place will touch — and
          we build the brief from their reality, not from precedent.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase">
        <div class="phase__num">PH / 02</div>
        <div class="phase__name">Vision</div>
        <div class="phase__desc">
          A sharpened, defendable point of view on what the space must become — and why it
          matters now. This is where ambition gets articulated in a form that survives
          contact with reality.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase">
        <div class="phase__num">PH / 03</div>
        <div class="phase__name">Master Planning</div>
        <div class="phase__desc">
          Translating vision into a buildable, fundable, operable plan across all five
          pillars simultaneously — so spatial, technology, brand, content and time decisions
          reinforce rather than contradict one another.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase">
        <div class="phase__num">PH / 04</div>
        <div class="phase__name">Realisation</div>
        <div class="phase__desc">
          Holding the line from groundbreaking through opening and into ongoing operation.
          We stay close enough to protect intent, and step back early enough that the
          client's team can run it.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
